comments: Rozier (CHA) makes some contact with Smith Jr.'s (CHA) side during the drive but contact does not affect his ability to defend.
Randle (NYK) makes marginal contact to Rozier's (CHA) body during his driving shot but does not affect his ability to finish.
Graham (CHA) briefly grasps Randle (NYK) as they disengage from the pick but contact does not affect his FOM.
Gibson (NYK) makes contact with Washington (CHA) off ball that does not affect his ability to defend the drive shot attempt.
Barrett (NYK) places a hand to Graham's (CHA) front at the start of his drive that affects his SQBR.
Graham (CHA) establishes legal position in Gibson's (NYK) path during the screen and absorbs the contact.
Washington (CHA) makes marginal contact with Randle's (NYK) body during his shooting motion but contact does not affect his drive shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) makes marginal contact with Washington (CHA) prior to the pick but contact does not affect his FOM.
Ntilikina (NYK) makes contact and clamps Washignton's (CHA) arm in the post that affects his FOM.
Morris (NYK) makes contact to Washignton's (CHA) arm during his shooting motion that affects his drive shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) engages with Graham (CHA) during the pick but contact does not affect his ability to defend.
Washington (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs contact created by Randle (NYK) during his driving shot attempt.
Williams (CHA) briefly grasps Gibson's (NYK) side during the rebound but contact does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Washington (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in Morris Sr.'s (NYK) path and makes marginal contact during the screen that does not affect his ability to defend.
Ntilikina (NYK) makes incidental "high five" contact to Graham's (CHA) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) makes contact with Randle (NYK) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
